The All Progressives Congress(APC) in Ondo State has fixed February 2, 2021, for the commencement of membership registration and revalidation. It was gathered the date for the exercise was fixed after a meeting on Wednesday evening. Acting Spokesman of the party, Alex Kalejaiye, who confirmed the date, said those to carry put the exercise have been inaugurated and were currently undergoing training. Kalejaiye said awareness would be carried out to sensitize the public on the need to join the APC.